Class IdentificationFeaturesCache

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.compomics.util.experiment.identification.features.IdentificationFeaturesCache

  • public class IdentificationFeaturesCache
extends Object
    This class caches the identification features calculated by the IdentificationFeaturesGenerator for later reuse.

    Marc Vaudel
